data.attachments: A list of attachment names separated by commas
data.author: The User ID of the user who sent the message
data.channelId: The channel with the #. This must be the same as the folder name
data.content: Embeds is the number of embeds on the message. Content is where the message content goes
Message json files must be named messages-XX.json where XX is two digits.
Messages are ordered from newest to oldest
